### Send OTP
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/otp/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "+1234567890"
}

### Verify OTP
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/otp/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "+1234567890",
  "code": "123456"
}

### Get Profile (requires token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Update Profile (requires token)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/user/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "firstName": "John Updated",
  "lastName": "Doe Updated",
  "phoneNumber": "+1234567890"
}

### Upload KYC Document (requires token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/kyc/upload-document
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "documentType": "passport",
  "documentUrl": "https://example.com/document.jpg"
}

